      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AGON CARAMEL (7) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Scored by 2.5 lengths last time (25.99) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 450m at this track. Rates a leading player. MORAINE QUINN (4) dropped out early but wound up strongly and charged into the minors when a 2 length third (22.82) at this track in Grade 5. Ready to find winning form. PAW LAMPADES (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Horsham over 410m (23.79). Returns to a course where he has performed well. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. POWER AFFECT (8) can sneak into the finish.",
